{"tags":["fedora","vpn","fortify","forticlient vpn"],"category":"linux","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因為工作的關係，有時會需要連回公司處理事情，而公司使用的是 FortiCllient VPN，平常上班都是使用公司的 Windows 筆電連接，想說來試試看能不能在 Fedora 中使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"使用gnome設定app"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用GNOME「設定」APP"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 Fedora 41 Workstation中，設定值→網路中已經有內建的VPN工具可以連接 FortiClient VPN 伺服器："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"922/X0Ehlq.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"點一下「VPN」旁的「+」號："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"922/EJhLhj.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接著點擊「Multi-protocal VPN Client (openconnect)」："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"924/zlJeel.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"輸入vpn設定值"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"輸入VPN設定值"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"接著切換到「身份」頁籤，在「VPN Protocal」下拉選單中選擇「Fortinet SSL VPN」，並輸入VPN建置人員提供的資訊，像是通訊閘（也就是對應VPN Server的URL），若有客製的port號，就一併輸入在通訊閘。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最後取一個自己能夠辨認的名稱並按下「套用」，VPN設定就完成了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"使用vpn"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用VPN"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用的方式也很簡單，直接按旁邊的開關，或是從GNOME的系統閘之中也能開啟："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"922/WgqEvJ.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"開啟之後會出現一個登入小視窗，打上VPN建置人員提供的帳號與密碼，按下「Login」就完成囉。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"922/HOle2r.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若啟用成功，GNOME系統圖示會多出一個鎖頭，就代表目前已經連上VPN。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"article-img","props":{"img":"922/N15wYG.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"後記"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"後記"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在剛開始嘗試設定時，找到的資料是使用"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"openfortivpn"}]},{"type":"text","value":"這個套件，但過程中遇到很多問題，結果在查詢解法的過程中發現可以使用原本就內建的"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"openconnect"}]},{"type":"text","value":"來連線，而且步驟少了很多，非常方便。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"當然也試過官方提供的rpm套件，但根本連不上XD。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"使用gnome設定app","depth":2,"text":"使用GNOME「設定」APP","children":[{"id":"輸入vpn設定值","depth":3,"text":"輸入VPN設定值"},{"id":"使用vpn","depth":3,"text":"使用VPN"}]},{"id":"後記","depth":2,"text":"後記"}]}}}